
Podcast via https://theblockchainsocialist.com/ccg-chronicles-8-token-engineering-and-holochain/

=Description=

"This episode is a continuation of the CCG Chronicles series which is a collection of interviews conducted during the Crypto Commons Gathering (CCG) in Austria back in August 2021. The interviews were also filmed to potentially be a part of a documentary I’m making with a few others.

During the CCG I interviewed Scott Morris (@CS_Morris) and Moritz Bierling (@bierlingm) about how to design a new currency system, blockchain vs. holochain, and memes. Scott is a currency design consultant  working in both crypto and non-crypto based currencies focused on cooperative finance. We talked a bit about a TedX talk he gave titled “Putting people and the planet before paper wealth“. Moritz works a lot in the Holochain ecosystem. "

